      "author": "wmwby",
      "description": "## What's New\n\n### Multi-language Autocomplete Framework\n- Introduced a multi-language autocomplete framework supporting Chinese, English, Japanese, and Korean\n- Added Japanese and Korean LaTeX keyword mappings\n- Language auto-detection based on Obsidian locale settings\n\n### Documentation\n- Split README into Chinese and English bilingual versions\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/wmwby/obsidian-easy-latex/compare/1.0.1...1.3.0",
